== About ==
'''<nowiki>{{font}}</nowiki>''' is used to define text styles, for example, size and color. It can also be used to inject [[CSS]]. This can be useful when needed to change "I" in Arial to "{{font|I|font=Times}}" in Times, since in Arial, uppercase "I" looks the same as lowercase "L".

== Use ==
<code><nowiki>{{font|TEXT(or「text=TEXT」)|font=FONT|size=SIZE（px/em/pt/%）|color=COLOR|bgcolor=BACKGROUND COLOR|css=CSS}}</nowiki></code>

